{
  "texts": [
    "It is a transformer-based architecture with the ability to generate text based on patterns learned from vast amounts of data during its training phase 50.",
    "As the goal of our study was to test the model's generalization capabilities in a zero-shot context, we did not fine-tune it for this specific task.",
    "In the initial stage of our approach, using API access, the model was prompted with a question of whether it was familiar with the Social Phobia Inventory (SPIN 42, 43) and how it is scored.",
    "The model responded affirmatively, indicating that data related to the SPIN 42, 43 have been used during its training phase.",
    "Due to OpenAI`s policy of not disclosing the specific datasets used during training, we were unable to verify this further."
  ]
}